Westinghouse WHSSBBS02 Sterilizer (White) Price: Rs.2690

Westinghouse WHSSBBS02-GS Elect Steam Sterilizer - Life is precious and so
column15: it becomes inevitable that everything in our life is clean and healthy. This is even more important if you are nursing an infant who deserves optimum care and hygiene. The Westinghouse Electric Steam Sterilizer WHSSBBS02-GS is the answer to your child feeding woes. You can store milk bottles and milk pump sterilizer in the Westinghouse Electric Steam Sterilizer for the most hygienic and bacteria free milk feeding for your baby. The electric steam bottle sterilizer can take up to six sets of most milk bottle available in the market both fat and thin bottles. It operates easily through a single switch and has a power indicator light and high power heating element for an effective sterilizing cycle. You can keep your things inside the Westinghouse Electric Steam Sterilizer WHSSBBS02-GS and let it run for 10 minutes and they will remain sterile for at least 3 hours. The electric steam sterilizer can also sterilize breast milk pump accessories. This product is good for dry boil protection and is convertible for use in microwave ovens with option trays. You can use stainless steel heating element for optimum hygiene. Westinghouse WHSSBBS02-GS Electric Steam Sterilizer Key Features are - Sterilize for 10 minutes and keep the contents sterile for 3 hours
